urlrunner is a simple tool for OSX to allow local linking to files through a browser.
To open a file, hold shift and click a link.
Otherwise it will open Finder and select it.

It accepts file urls like this:

	urlrunner:///Volumes/
	urlrunner:///Users/arzynik/Desktop/dw.txt

Created by Devin Smith for Luma Pictures (lumapictures.com).